text: EDH is a big-ass game and there's a lot of room to write about a lot of things, even the tire-fire that is the biggest mistake in commander history, partners.
If Partners has required you team with another that shares at least a color, would it have been as bad?
Wedges and Shards instead of 4C?
They needed something to narrow them down, yeah. Partner With is neat, and I'm sure there's some other permutation that would work as well.

Creating 4-5 generically useful in every situation cards in strong colors that can be paired with another generically useful card in strong colors was only really ever gonna wind up with one outcome, and it's the one we have today.
Which to be clear is fine if that's your jam. I think they're a tire-fire, but if someone likes them it doesn't stop me from doing my thing.
